      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should reach out, but what's the point? talking about it doesn't make the house less empty. it doesn't make me feel less like a shell of a person. it just feels like i'm dragging this heavy, broken thing called a life around for no reason at all. everything is just... empty.",
